latestPosts.caption:
In the mood for some culture 💕
.
I’ve always had a special spot for the quintessential Gujarati Kediyu. It’s cute, flowy, dancy and pretty versatile. Basically a peplum jacket. My personal fav is the one that’s crafted with patchwork. This one is from @_kinchecom, a brand that recycles old fabrics into new kediyus. A quiet celebration of the humble adorable silhouette. 
.
Topped it with this rad @stellamccartney bag from @ajioluxe 💙
.
#indianstyle #indianfashion #stellamccartneybag
